<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l35"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> geſagt / vvie Jr ew vormals darynne gar <expan>freuntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l36">beweiſet vnd gemüet habt <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / des vvir ew <expan>fleiſʒıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l37">vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">ew </del> <expan>fürb<ex>aʒ</ex></expan> aber <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hilff vnd <expan>fürdr<ex>ung</ex></expan> darcʒu tun wöllet daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l38"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſein pferd wıdervverde / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
